reviewText: Very good moivie for little girls plus they like to smell the scratch and sniff
I grew up watching this I've seen it 4 times,and love it! I think it teaches kids to be there very best,and to find a place where you fit in
my thirteen year old grand daughter tea loves this movie alot because its full of colors and lots of music and fashion.
My five year old little girl likes this movie.  I did notice its not one of her favorites that she requests over and over.
I purchased this dvd for my 7 year old daughters. They watched it and loved it. They have repeatedly watched the movie. They enjoyed the bright colors in the movie and the characters.
My daughter is 3 yrs old and she LOVES this movie. I like the message it gives her and the songs are great for her to sing. The story line is predictable but it is perfect for her age.
If your girl likes Yummy Land Dolls then she'll need this DVD.  Cute story
My daughter loves the yummi land dolls and was ecstatic when I got this for her for a 'good job in school' reward. Very cute movie.. Thumbs up.
My daughter is 3 and got this for Christmas. She loves it. Very cute movie.
